358
00:59:44,639 --> 00:59:47,519
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam te čuo četvrti, Discord, Telegram, Twitter i?

359
00:59:48,880 --> 00:59:49,199
[SPEAKER_00] Reddit.

360
00:59:49,679 --> 00:59:50,639
[SPEAKER_01] Aha, Reddit, OK.

361
00:59:51,360 --> 00:59:52,159
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, Reddit.

362
00:59:53,920 --> 00:59:59,599
[SPEAKER_01] I tamo ste zapravo komunicirali, tamo ste komunicirali svoj initial coin offering, jel tako?

363
