365
01:00:02,480 --> 01:00:02,639
[SPEAKER_01] Hm.

366
01:00:02,719 --> 01:00:02,880
[SPEAKER_01] Hm.

367
01:00:03,280 --> 01:00:03,440
[SPEAKER_01] Hm.

368
01:00:05,440 --> 01:00:05,679
[SPEAKER_01] Hm.

369
01:00:06,400 --> 01:00:06,480
